      {
        "type": "preformatted",
        "text": "All swans are white.",
        "spans": []
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "However, if you have observed even one black swan, you should not come to this conclusion. Instead, you might draw one of the weaker conclusions:",
        "spans": [
          {
            "start": 79,
            "end": 89,
            "type": "hyperlink",
